Di leǧwahi-nni i gezdeɣ Bubliyus lḥakem ameqqran n tmurt n Ityubya, țemyezwaǧen-nsen kan akk-d lemfaṣel nniḍen i gḥekkmen tamurt-nni !
Akken daɣen i glaq ad xedmen deg wulawen-nsen : m'ara d-banen leɛquṛ, m'ara heggit iman-nsen seg yimi n ddunit ;
Ma yella yewwi-d lḥal ad iṭṭef amkan anda ara yali wass, m'ara kkun-yefk ula d kunwi aț-țṛuẓuḥem ula d kunwi.
Acḥal n tikkal i glaqen a t-tɛiwnem, meɛna qeblet iwakken aț-țɛiwnem kra n wussan m'ara d-yaweḍ.
Lameɛna tella daɣen yiwet n twaɣyin ( ticiṭwin ) n tezliwteḍ-nni ; ilaq a d-tbeggen acḥal ɣas akken ilaq, acḥal ihi i d-tfeǧǧeǧen n yiṭij.
Llant gar-asent si tmurt n Kenɛan, llant gar-asen win i d-yusan si tejmaɛt n Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin-nsen.
Eɛni m'ara tebɣuḍ aț-țṛuḥeḍ nekkini di temdint n Kenɛan, iwakken aț-țkecmeḍ ɣer tmurt n wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt n Qirya, m'ara ṛuḥen ad awin iman-ik.
Deg yiwet n tezduɣin, tella daɣen yiwet n tbuqalt.
Axaṭer lḥukkam n Ṛuman i ț-țamdint ur nebɛid ara ɣef temdint n Ninebi, neɣ m'ulac amettel iman-is ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, armi d ɣuṛ-es.
ad ɛeggṛet i webrid n Ṛebbi akk-d lewḥuc di lebḥeṛ, a d-tebɛen !
Yewweḍ-ed lweqt anda i țɛeggiden di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen aṭas n Lmasiḥ yellan d lɛid n Lǧameɛ iqedsen ; mkul ass i deg ara d-tban tmanegt n Sidna Ɛisa.
Aṭas n iyunaniyen i gellan d leɛwayed n Lmasiḥ akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ akk-d wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ yellan di ddunit.
Yuɣ lḥal tella dinna yiwet n tikkelt i deg ițbecciṛ imensi n lɛid n Tuffɣa, aṭas n lweqt i deg ara d-yasen deffir-es.
Yezmer lḥal ad immeslay ɣef temẓal n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ț-țameddit, lameɛna iwakken a d-tban acḥal yiwet n tikkelt kan, yeɛni ass n uɛebbuḍ n uẓaṛ.
Di mkul ass n westeɛfu, tajmaɛt n wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețnejmaɛen di țnaṣfa n wass wis xemsin, m'ara ț-țijmuyaɛ n imasiḥiyen yellan di mkul amkan cwiṭ i d-ițmeslayen, neṣbeṛ i ḥeggu n Lmasiḥ.
Wid akk yellan deg webrid n Ṛebbi i gețnuq yid-es, ṣubben-d ɣuṛ-sen s lewḥuc di lebḥeṛ, iwakken a d-beḥten leɛḍ.
Imi i ten-issewlen si leɛzay n lebḥeṛ, ur zmiren ara ad ṛuḥen ɣer tmurt n Mačči ɣef lmeṛṣa n at Isṛail.
Seg yiwen wergaz i d-yusan si tmurt n Gulguṭa, aṭas n wid ițemyezwaṭayen akk-d yezgaren, ulli, iɛewdiwen, ikeṛṛusen leḥwayeǧ n lewḥuceṛ ; leḥwayeǧ akk iteddun !
M'ara tedduklem ɣer yiwet n tmurt n Tamurt neɣ di lebḥeṛ, a d-yas wass-nni ! Iḍ-agi aț-țuɣalem di luluf n lebḥeṛ, neɣ m'ara d-yaweḍ iṭij.
D wagi i d sebba n tuccḍa, ẓran a d-yas wass i deg ara yali Aurora nniḍen, am akken yella igenwan m'ara d-iɛeddin kra n wayen yellan deg-sen.
Akken daɣen i gella di leqṛun alamma ț-țudrin, tafat ur tezmirem ara a d-teḥyum ula d kunwi iwakken aț-țɛicem di tegmawin.
Di yal amkan n tmurt n Jawhar, llan wid yețwaxedmen s tuffra, d acu i glaqen a d-tbeggen acḥal d acu ara xedmen wiyaḍ.
Ur țɛeggiden ara ayen xeddmen, beggnet-ed s tɛeqcin, iwakken ad țemcawaṛen wway gar-asen ɣef ddemma n yisem-nsen neɣ ad xedmen akken i t-ɛeqcin.
Lexbeṛ-agi n lxiṛ i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i Sidi Ṛebbi, ur ilaq ara a d-isbeggen lecɣal-nsen.
Iqeddacen daɣen ilaq-asen ad țțaɣen awal iwakken ad ɛeǧben bab-nsen, ur sen-țeddun ara di nneqma, ad țțaɣen awal.
